Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:10.91,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,在这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:11.50,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,别让她们跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:13.11,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,从西边包围
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.11,0:00:14.21,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,把她们逼到悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:16.49,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,包围她们！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:26.79,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:29.11,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,没事的 尤特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:30.10,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.19,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:33.57,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,那边是悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:41.90,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,她们跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:42.64,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}她们在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:44.05,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂！在这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:46.80,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}别让她们跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.41,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:58.94,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,没关系的 尤特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:00.87,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,你没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:03.66,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}杀了他们！把她们都杀了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.23,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}烧死她们！                                   把她们干掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.94,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,为什么 妈妈 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:11.55,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,因为大家都很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:13.18,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,害怕我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:16.48,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,他们害怕的东西与我们相同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.28,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,所以你没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.49,0:01:26.99,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,尤特 你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:32.57,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,不要啊 这种事情不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.86,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,没事的 尤特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.30,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:38.40,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:40.14,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,我爱你
