Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.99,Undead 标题,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960, 1050)\blur5\fs125\fad(450, 0)}狼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.49,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,竟然有狼出没 这可不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:35.15,ep2屏字,,0,0,0,,{\fad(290, 0)\an7\fsp10\fs100\pos(432,778)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}德国南部
