Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.20,ep2屏字,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fsp20\fs100\pos(700,778)\c&H000000&}施内塔尔站
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.46,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到施内塔尔站
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.11,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,二位是来观光的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.22,Undead Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,是来驱逐怪物的
